&#xa0;
[normal]The Equal Rights Trust – Written evidence[bold]&#xa0;[bold]About the Equal Rights Trust[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The Equal Rights Trust (ERT) is an independent international human rights organisation whose purpose is to combat discrimination and promote equality as a fundamental human right and a basic principle of social justice. ERT focuses on the complex relationship between different types of discrimination, developing strategies for translating the principles of equality into practice.
[normal]&#xa0;
